{"tid":1674782,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人仲記唔記得畫家？","createTime":"2019-10-25T11:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T11:35:24.000Z","uid":251732,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"30b5a83b17afc025167992fc0c9215aa92d109a8","tid":1674782,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T11:56:20.000Z","msg":"由呢個抗爭起義嘅開端起， 畫家作為資深抗爭者， 612 前後已經全面落曬力參與成個抗爭運動， 直至到因為圍狗屋嗰單嘢畀人重判廿幾條罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n更加唔洗講二千幾個畀狗咬嘅手足， 以及無數被人間蒸發及慘死嘅小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n 所以更加唔好因為條例收咗皮就咁算， 革命鬥真係要經歷好長時間， 因為我哋要為受苦難嘅香港小朋友報仇， 從而彰顯當權冇辦法實踐嘅公義 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n解散警隊 刻不容緩<br />\n香港人 反抗 <br />\n天滅中共 全黨死清光"},{"pid":"66ba25a36357d34dbb3a857ad3278fd43ddc3ca9","tid":1674782,"uid":61334,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:03:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12c90d72c2cc02e96d87ab73b487022e2bfdd971","tid":1674782,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:04:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74b3c551c4b91cb9c3ea1edfad72ec350f494013","tid":1674782,"uid":279356,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:06:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e9vztW4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe9vztW4.gif&h=8b1249aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f94d63e4e394d3a87a9aab010e51753af1133b10","tid":1674782,"uid":19984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:14:16.000Z","msg":"我宣布，十點鐘鳩嗌，正式回歸！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1674226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1674226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"23a629947988edc4a598aeac0f481d9f1323b7ed","tid":1674782,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T12:16:10.000Z","msg":"一推"},{"pid":"299ed4b9d19a63